<div class="columns small-8">
<p class="small"><strong>Peta Greenfield</strong></p>
<p class="small description">Peta Greenfield holds a PhD in Classics and Ancient History and led a secondary English department for seven years. She is the co-host and co-producer of The Partial Historians podcast and thrives in translating research for public understanding.</p>
