<div class="columns small-8">
<p class="small"><strong>Janelle Evans</strong></p>
<p class="small description">Janelle Evans (Dharug) is an exhibiting artist, writer and curator based in Melbourne. She is Head of the Master of Contemporary Arts degree at Victorian College of the Arts, University of Melbourne and also lectures in Critical and Arts Theories. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row innercontent">
<div class="columns small-4 thumb">
