</div>
<div class="columns small-8">
<p class="small"><strong>Kate Constantine</strong></p>
<p class="small description">Konstantina (Kate Constantine) is a proud Gadigal woman of the Eora nation and a neo-contemporary Indigenous artist. She is re-imagining the traditions of her peoples’ dot painters, providing a modern narrative to better understand a First Nations perspective of Australia.</p>
</div>
</div>
