<div class="teaser columns small-12 left-post-thumbnail widget">
<a href="https://blog.degruyter.com/cyberattacks-on-cultural-heritage-institutions/" title="Our Website Is Currently Unavailable: Cyberattacks on Cultural Heritage Institutions">
<div class="shadow"></div>
<div class="img" style="background-image:url('https://blog.degruyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/trojan-horse-640x800.jpg')"></div>
<article>
<header>
<p>Academia &amp; Publishing</p>
<h2>Our Website Is Currently Unavailable: Cyberattacks on Cultural Heritage Institutions</h2>
</header>
<footer><div class="post-meta"><span class="show-for-medium">Tamara Štefanac | </span>12.04.2024</div></footer>
</article>
</a>
</div>
<div class="teaser columns small-12 left-post-thumbnail widget">
<a href="https://blog.degruyter.com/wie-steht-es-um-das-wissenschaftliche-erbe-der-ddr-eine-podiumsdiskussion/" title="Wie steht es um das wissenschaftliche Erbe der DDR? Eine Podiumsdiskussion">
<div class="shadow"></div>
<div class="img" style="background-image:url('https://blog.degruyter.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Fotothek_df_roe-neg_0006076_030_Messebesucher_am_Stand_des_Akademie-Verlags_Berlin.jpg')"></div>
<article>
